# ChangeLog for media-sound/perljammer
# Copyright 1999-2012 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: $

*perljammer-1.8.5 (08 MAR 2016)
  08 MAR 2016; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>:
  Restrict mirrors.  Fix UTF8 support.

*perljammer-1.8.4 (01 SEP 2015)
  01 SEP 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>:
  Fix all of the UTF8 handling issues.

*perljammer-1.8.3 (07 MAY 2015)
  07 MAY 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>:
  Fixed errorfont and allowed errorfont to be set from the config file, defaulting
  to boldfont if not set

*perljammer-1.8.2 (21 APR 2015)
  21 APR 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>:
  Fixed several missing -font specifications on text buttons after the default font
  suddenly stopped working for no obvious reason.

*perljammer-1.8.1-r1 (17 FEB 2015)
  17 FEB 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>:
  Fixed a bug in RemoteJammer's skin selection logic.

*perljammer-1.8.1 (17 FEB 2015)
  17 FEB 2015; Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>:
  Initial overlay creation.  Ebuild submitted by Phil Stracchino <phils@caerllewys.net>
